%% Migration process. See 05-jkiss-migration-plan.md
flowchart TB
  Scan[inventory: SCAN + classifyKeys] --> Owned[tenant-owned keys]
  Owned --> Loop[for each key in bounded batches]
  Loop --> Exists{target t:jkiss:key exists?}
  Exists -- no --> Copy[dry-run? count : SET target = legacy value]
  Exists -- yes --> Eq{checksum equal?}
  Eq -- yes --> Skip[skip - idempotent]
  Eq -- no --> Conflict[record CONFLICT - never overwrite]
  Copy --> Next[next key]
  Skip --> Next
  Conflict --> Next
  Next --> Verify[verify: every owned key has matching copy]
  Verify --> Done[legacy keys NEVER deleted]
